FIG. 1 is an isometric view of a sheet of thermoplastic material which is at least partially saturated with an ink constituent prior to forming an image on the medium;


FIG. 2 is a top plate view of the pre-inked thermoplastic medium of the present invention being processed by a thermal head printer;


